0.title: Introduction

1.body: This chapter walks you through setting up a basic NixOS system. We'll aim to create a system setup comparable to a standard Linux distribution Flake Why Flakes? Flakes provide a structured way to manage configurations, packages, and environments in NixOS. They enable reproducible builds, improve modularity, and offer a cleaner workflow for managing system and user configurations.
